data.description: Welcome Home to 304 Rosemore! You can unwind on either the front porch or the private back porch. The house has plenty of space for entertaining, featuring a large living area with hardwood floors and a cozy fireplace. The dining room also has hardwood flooring, and the kitchen boasts granite countertops, providing ample space for food prep and entertaining. The primary suite is on the main level featuring 2 walk-in closets, and a spacious bathroom with a jetted tub and a separate shower. Upstairs, there are 2 additional guest rooms and a bonus room. New roof 2024 and new hvac 2022.
